---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — GrabTube">
  <h1>About GrabTube</h1>
  <div class="prose card">
    <p>
      GrabTube is a fast, sleek front-end for downloading YouTube videos as MP4 or extracting MP3
      audio — complete with the title, author, and cover art embedded in the file. Paste a single
      video or a whole playlist; we hand the heavy lifting to a dedicated conversion service and give
      you back a clean file (or a tidy ZIP for playlists).
    </p>
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      The website you are looking at is fully static — there is no server, no database, and no
      account system here. When you start a download, your browser talks directly to a separate,
      configurable conversion service that does the actual extraction and packaging. Nothing about
      your activity is stored on this site.
    </p>
    <h2>Responsible use</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      GrabTube is a tool. You are responsible for complying with applicable copyright law and with
      the terms of service of any platform you download from. Please only download content you have
      the right to use. GrabTube does not host, store, or distribute any copyrighted material.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-400);
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
